  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/08/after-babys-death-kentucky-parents-sue-infant-formula-maker-at-center-of-2022-crisis.webp" alt="After baby's death, Kentucky parents sue infant formula maker at center of 2022 crisis"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">After baby's death, Kentucky parents sue infant formula maker at center of 2022 crisis</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The parents of a Kentucky baby who died last fall after drinking bacteria-tainted infant formula are the latest to sue Abbott Nutrition, the manufacturer at the heart of a 2022 crisis that left millions of Americans scrambling to feed their children.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/08/after-babys-death-kentucky-parents-sue-infant-formula-maker-at-center-of-2022-crisis/"  >(JONEL ALECCIA, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 10 Aug 2024 01:25:34 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 10 Aug 2024 01:25:34 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="DAVID SHARP, MICHAEL HILL, MARK SCOLFORO and PATRICK WHITTLE, Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/10/debby-bringing-heavy-rain-flooding-and-possible-tornadoes-northeast-into-the-weekend.webp" alt="Flooding from the remnants of Debby leads to high water rescues in New York, Pennsylvania"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Flooding from the remnants of Debby leads to high water rescues in New York, Pennsylvania</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      First responders launched high-water and helicopter rescues of people trapped in cars and homes in rural New York and Pennsylvania as heavy rain from the remnants of Debby slammed the Northeast with intense floods.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/10/debby-bringing-heavy-rain-flooding-and-possible-tornadoes-northeast-into-the-weekend/"  >(DAVID SHARP, MICHAEL HILL, MARK SCOLFORO and PATRICK WHITTLE, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 21:13:04 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 11 Aug 2024 21:13:04 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Sara Filips, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/11/disney-world-announces-cars-monsters-inc-expansions-at-parks.webp" alt="Disney World announces 'Cars,' 'Monsters, Inc.' expansions at parks"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Disney World announces 'Cars,' 'Monsters, Inc.' expansions at parks</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Disney World has made a huge announcement regarding several expansion plans coming to three of their four theme parks.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/11/disney-world-announces-cars-monsters-inc-expansions-at-parks/"  >(Sara Filips, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 09 Aug 2024 22:46:38 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 09 Aug 2024 22:46:38 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
