      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/10/ted-bundys-cousin-shares-chilling-moment-she-knew-he-monster.webp" alt="Ted Bundy's cousin shares 'chilling moment' she knew he 'was a monster'"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ted Bundy's cousin shares 'chilling moment' she knew he 'was a monster'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Edna Cowell Martin, Ted Bundy&apos;s cousin, is the first of the serial killer&apos;s relatives to write a book about her experience growing up with the notorious serial killer.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/10/ted-bundys-cousin-shares-chilling-moment-she-knew-he-monster/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 16:07:15 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 16:07:15 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Amber Coakley, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/08/watch-live-giant-pandas-to-make-public-debut-at-san-diego-zoo-during-opening-ceremony.webp" alt="WATCH: Giant pandas make public debut at San Diego Zoo"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">WATCH: Giant pandas make public debut at San Diego Zoo</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      It's officially "Panda Day" in California, with the San Diego Zoo just hours away from revealing two giant pandas in a historic moment of diplomacy between the U.S. and China.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/08/watch-live-giant-pandas-to-make-public-debut-at-san-diego-zoo-during-opening-ceremony/"  >(Amber Coakley, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
