        <div class="row"><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:28:11 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:28:11 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="CIO">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/tech/2024/08/09/the-role-of-accelerated-computing-in-reducing-energy-consumption.webp" alt="The role of accelerated computing in reducing energy consumption"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The role of accelerated computing in reducing energy consumption</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Businesses increasingly rely on powerful computing systems housed in data centers for their workloads. As the data center market expands, at an estimated growth rate of 10.5% from 2024 to 20301, energy consumption has become a major concern.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/09/the-role-of-accelerated-computing-in-reducing-energy-consumption/"  >(CIO)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 17:55:55 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 17:55:55 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Dominick Mastrangelo, The Hill">
