      <img src="/static9/tech/2024/08/08/warren-sanders-castro-sports-streaming.webp" alt="Warren, Sanders, Castro urge DOJ to probe joint streamed sports venture"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Warren, Sanders, Castro urge DOJ to probe joint streamed sports venture</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A group of congressional Democrats is urging the Department of Justice (DOJ) and Federal Communications Commission (FCC) to probe a planned joint streaming sports venture by some of the nation's largest media conglomerates. Warner Bros. Discovery, Fox Corp. and The Walt Disney Co.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/08/warren-sanders-castro-sports-streaming/"  >(Dominick Mastrangelo, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
