    <h3 itemprop="headline">Elon Musk sues OpenAI, renewing claims ChatGPT-maker put profits before 'the benefit of humanity'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      LOS ANGELES (AP) — Elon Musk filed a lawsuit on Monday against OpenAI and two of its founders, Sam Altman and Greg Brockman, renewing claims that the ChatGPT-maker betrayed its founding aims of benefiting the public good rather than pursuing profits.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/05/elon-musk-sues-openai-renewing-claims-chatgpt-maker-put-profits-before-the-benefit-of-humanity/"  >(SARAH PARVINI, Associated Press, KRON4)</a>
