    <h3 itemprop="headline">State GOP leader calls Harris-Walz agenda &#8216;extreme,&#8217; out of touch with rural voters</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      “I think that he does very minimal to reach out across the aisle or directly,” Demuth said. “So I don’t think that plays very well, especially in greater Minnesota, when they hear that he is not available and willing to work for all Minnesotans.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/09/state-gop-leader-calls-harriswalz-agenda-extreme-out-of-touch-with-rural-voters/"  >(Cathy Wurzer and Gracie  Stockton, MPR News)</a>
