    <h3 itemprop="headline">US surgeon general was warned by his mom to avoid politics, but he jumped into the fray anyway</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Surgeon General Vivek Murthy isn’t shying away from politics, as his mother had once hoped when he was a kid.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/11/us-surgeon-general-was-warned-by-his-mom-to-avoid-politics-but-he-jumped-into-the-fray-anyway/"  >(Amanda Seitz, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
